{"word":"G112 - ἄθεος - átheos - ath'-eh-os - Without God","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἄθεος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">átheos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ath'-eh-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Without God</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தேவனற்ற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"without God, knowing and worshipping no God"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1 - Α - A - al'-fah/1\">G1</a> (as a negative particle) and <a href=\"#/G2316 - θεός - theós - theh'-os/2316\">G2316</a>; <i>godless:</i> - without God.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G112/112\">G112</a>, <a href=\"#/G2304/2304\">G2304</a>, <a href=\"#/G2305/2305\">G2305</a>, <a href=\"#/G2312/2312\">G2312</a>, <a href=\"#/G2316/2316\">G2316</a>, <a href=\"#/G2320/2320\">G2320</a>"}]}